        "descriptions": [
          {
            "description": [
              {
                "text": "Carl, Greg and Anne work for WaterSonic Corporation. Recently, the company has come up with an idea for a new electric toothbrush."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Carl: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I think we've "
            },
            {
              "mark": "come up with a winner"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Anne: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I agree. The new Brush-o-matic should be a "
            },
            {
              "mark": "blockbuster"
            },
            {
              "text": "!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Carl: ",
              "text": "Our designers have already made up some prototypes. The toothbrushes have a tooth-whitening attachment and many other "
            },
            {
              "mark": "bells and whitles"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Greg: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We should "
            },
            {
              "mark": "fast track a project"
            },
            {
              "text": ". Let's try to launch it in time for the holiday season."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Ane: "
            },
            {
              "text": "This will be a great "
            },
            {
              "mark": "stocking stuffer"
            },
            {
              "text": "!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Carl: "
            },
            {
              "text": "We definitely need a "
            },
            {
              "mark": "big win"
            },
            {
              "text": " for the holidays."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Anne: "
            },
            {
              "text": "This is a great idea. We're going to "
            },
            {
              "mark": "make a killing"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Greg: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Let's not talk about this project to anybody who doesn't need to know. We'll "
            },
            {
              "mark": "keep it under wraps"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Carl: "
            },
            {
              "text": "I agree. "
            },
            {
              "mark": "Mum's the word"
            },
            {
              "text": " ."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "text": "We don't want any of our competitors to "
            },
            {
              "mark": "get wind of"
            },
            {
              "text": " the idea and "
            },
            {
              "mark": "rip it off"
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "lineBreak": true,
          "paragraph": [
            {
              "boldText": "Anne: "
            },
            {
              "text": "Right. Let's meet again on Monday morning and discuss our "
            },
            {
              "mark": "game plan"
            },
            {
              "text": " for "
            },
            {
              "mark": "getting this project off the ground"
            },
            {
              "text": "!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
